To install everything, you might use:
cd /usr/local/bin; ln -s /usr/src/public/textutils-1.3/bin/* .
cd /usr/local/man/cat1; ln -s /usr/src/public/textutils-1.3/man/cat1/* .

To recompile, cd to textutils-1.3 and type 'make'.  Gcc should not
report any errors or warnings.  The default destination for the
execuatlbes is /usr/src/contrib/textutils-1.3/{bin,man}, though this
path is not compiled into the executables.

The sources are available by anonymous ftp from prep.ai.mit.edu in the
file /pub/gnu/textutils-1.3.tar.Z.

